3 (invoke/status commands)\ndeployment/                   # Deployment design and spec\ndesign.md                     # Design doc for AR-020 (pack command)\ngo.mod / go.sum               # Go module files\nidle-cleanup/                 # Idle cleanup module\nintegrations/                 # Integration design and spec\npkg/                          # Go packages\nproject.md                    # Project context document\nproposal.md                   # Proposal for AR-024 (DockerService)\npython-sdk/                   # Python SDK\nsandbox-orchestration/        # Sandbox orchestration module\nsession-routing/              # Session routing module\nsession-store/                # Session store module\ntasks.md                      # Root tasks file (AR-023: invoke/status)\ntest_spec.md                  # Test specification\ntesting/                      # Testing module\n```\n\n### Project purpose (from `project.md`):\nAgentCube is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents**. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic through session-aware proxies, and manages lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n**Tech Stack:**\n- Server: Go 1.24\n- CLI/SDK: Python >= 3.10\n- CLI framework: Typer (Python), Gin (Go)\n- Kubernetes: CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`)\n\n---\n\n## 2. Existing tasks.md Files and Format\n\n### Location of all tasks.md files:\n- **Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` (AR-023: invoke/status commands)\n- **Per-change:** `changes/AR-XXX/tasks.md` for AR-001 through AR-024\n\n### Tasks.md Format (from `tasks.md` root and `changes/AR-020/tasks.md`):\n\nThe format follows a consistent structure:\n\n```markdown\n# AR-XXX: Title вҖ” Tasks\n\n> **Module:** cmd/cli\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-XXX/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-XXX/design.md`, ...\n\n## T1. Task Title\n\n- [ ] 1.1 Sub-task description\n- [ ] 1.2 Sub-task description\n- [ ] Write test: test description\n\n**Verification:** command or condition that proves completion\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1 в”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җ T2 в”Җв”Җ T3\n     в””в”Җв”Җ T4 в”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n**Parallel execution:** description of which tasks can run in parallel\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n| # | Criterion | Command |\n|---|-----------|---------|\n| AC1 | description | `command` |\n```\n\n### AR-024 tasks.md is mostly empty (a skeleton):\n- File: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md`\n- Contains only the header section with Module/Language/Size/Precondition/Reference/Dependency fields\n- T1 section is blank (no sub-tasks filled in)\n- Task Dependencies section is blank\n- Acceptance Criteria table is empty\n\n---\n\n## 3. DockerService-Related Code and References\n\n### Main implementation:\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n\n**Current methods:**\n- `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n- `check_docker_available() -> bool` -- checks if Docker daemon is reachable\n- `build_image(dockerfile_path, context_path, image_name, tag, build_args) -> Dict[str, str]` -- builds image, returns metadata\n- `_format_size(size_bytes: int) -> str` -- human-readable size formatting\n- `push_image(image_tag, registry_url, username, password) -> Dict[str, str]` -- pushes to registry\n- `_docker_login_sdk(registry_url, username, password) -> bool` -- logs into registry\n- `_tag_image_sdk(source_image, target_image) -> bool` -- tags an image\n\n**Missing methods (per design doc):**\n- `get_image_info(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]` -- NOT YET IMPLEMENTED\n- `_get_image_info(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]` -- NOT YET IMPLEMENTED\n- `remove_image(image_name: str) -> bool` -- NOT YET IMPLEMENTED\n\n### Design document:\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/design.md`\n\nKey design principles:\n- Each method call independently creates `docker.from_env()` client (stateless, thread-safe)\n- All public methods return `Dict[str, Any]` or `bool`; exceptions propagate up\n- `_` prefixed methods are internal helpers\n- DockerService does NOT print errors or call `sys.exit()` -- all exceptions propagate to Runtime layer\n\n### Tests:\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py`\n\nExisting test classes:\n- `TestDockerServiceCheckDockerAvailableRunning`\n- `TestDockerServiceCheckDockerAvailableNotRunning`\n- `TestDockerServiceBuildImageSuccess`\n- `TestDockerServiceBuildImageWithProxy`\n- `TestDockerServiceBuildImageFailure`\n- `TestDockerServiceFormatSize*` (Bytes, KB, MB, GB)\n- `TestDockerService_PushImage_Success`\n- `TestDockerService_PushImage_WithCredentials`\n- `TestDockerService_PushImage_Failure`\n- `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Success`\n- `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Failure`\n- `TestDockerService_TagImageSdk_Success`\n\n### Callers of DockerService:\n- **BuildRuntime** (`cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`): uses `check_docker_available()` and `build_image()`\n- **PublishRuntime** (`cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`): uses `check_docker_available()`, `_docker_login_sdk()`, and `push_image()`\n\n---\n\n## 4. cmd/cli Module Structure\n\n**Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/`\n\n```\ncmd/cli/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ pyproject.toml              # Package config, dependencies, entry points\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ .gitignore\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ agentcube/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py             # __version__=\"0.1.0\", exports app and Runtimes\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ cli/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ main.py             # Typer app: pack, build, publish, invoke, status commands\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ models/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ pack_models.py      # MetadataOptions dataclass\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ runtime/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py         # Re-exports all Runtime classes\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ pack_runtime.py     # PackRuntime\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ build_runtime.py    # BuildRuntime (uses DockerService)\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ publish_runtime.py  # PublishRuntime (uses DockerService)\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ invoke_runtime.py   # InvokeRuntime\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ status_runtime.py   # StatusRuntime\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ services/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ metadata_service.py # AgentMetadata (Pydantic), MetadataService\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ docker_service.py   # DockerService\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ k8s_provider.py     # KubernetesProvider (Deployment + Service)\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ agentcube_provider.py # AgentCubeProvider (AgentRuntime CRD)\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ operations/\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ __init__.py\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ tests/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ cli/                    # CLI command tests\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ runtime/                # Runtime class tests\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ services/               # Service and provider tests\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ models/                 # Model tests\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ integration/            # E2E tests\nв””в”Җв”Җ examples/\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ hello-agent/            # Python example\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ math-agent/             # Python example\n    в””в”Җв”Җ java-agent/             # Java example\n```\n\n**Entry point:** `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n\n**CLI Commands:** `pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Documents, Stage Documents (ST-3), and Architecture Docs\n\n### Design documents found:\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` | AR-020: CLI pack command -- full design (798 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/design.md` | AR-024: DockerService encapsulation -- design (334 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md` | AR-023: CLI invoke/status commands -- design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/design.md` | CLI toolkit design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md` | Deployment design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md` | Session routing design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md` | Session store design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/code-execution/design.md` | Code execution design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/design.md` | Integrations design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md` | Idle cleanup design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/design.md` | Python SDK design |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md` | CI/CD design |\n\n### Spec documents:\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` | AR-023: invoke/status delta spec (273 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md` | AR-024: DockerService delta spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md` | CLI toolkit spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md` | Deployment spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md` | Session routing spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/spec.md` | Session store spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/code-execution/spec.md` | Code execution spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/spec.md` | Integrations spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md` | Idle cleanup spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/spec.md` | Python SDK spec |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/spec.md` | CI/CD spec |\n\n### ST-3 (Stage 3 - Design Complete) References:\nST-3 is referenced as a **precondition** in tasks.md files. It means \"Design stage completed.\" Found in:\n- AR-002 through AR-023 tasks.md files (20 files total)\n- AR-024 does NOT reference ST-3 (its tasks.md is a blank skeleton)\n\n### Change Request (AR) structure:\nEach `changes/AR-XXX/` directory contains:\n- `proposal.md` -- Problem statement, scope, alternatives\n- `design.md` -- Detailed architecture, data structures, API contracts\n- `delta-spec.md` -- Gherkin-style scenarios (some ARs)\n- `tasks.md` -- Task breakdown with checkboxes, dependency graph, acceptance criteria\n\n---\n\n## 6. Existing Service Patterns and Similar Service Wrappers\n\n### Service pattern (all services in `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/`):\n\n**Common pattern across all services:**\n1. `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)` -- stores verbose flag\n2. Stateless operation -- each method creates its own client/connection\n3. Exceptions propagate upward (no internal error printing or sys.exit)\n4. Return typed dicts or booleans\n\n### Service classes:\n\n#### 1. `MetadataService` (`metadata_service.py`)\n```python\nclass MetadataService:\n    METADATA_FILES: List[str] = [\"agent_metadata.yaml\", \"agent.yaml\", \"metadata.yaml\"]\n    \n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None\n    def load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> Optional[AgentMetadata]\n    def save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None\n    def update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata\n    def validate_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path) -> bool\n```\n\n#### 2. `DockerService` (`docker_service.py`)\n```python\nclass DockerService:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None\n    def check_docker_available(self) -> bool\n    def build_image(...) -> Dict[str, str]\n    def push_image(...) -> Dict[str, str]\n    def _docker_login_sdk(...) -> bool\n    def _tag_image_sdk(...) -> bool\n    def _format_size(size_bytes: int) -> str\n    # Missing: get_image_info, _get_image_info, remove_image\n```\n\n#### 3. `KubernetesProvider` (`k8s_provider.py`)\n```python\nclass KubernetesProvider:\n    def __init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False) -> None\n    def deploy_agent(...) -> Dict[str, Any]\n    def wait_for_deployment_ready(self, deployment_name: str, timeout: int = 120) -> None\n    def get_agent_status(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]\n    def delete_agent(self, agent_name: str) -> None\n```\n\n#### 4. `AgentCubeProvider` (`agentcube_provider.py`)\n```python\nclass AgentCubeProvider:\n    CRD_GROUP = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n    CRD_VERSION = \"v1alpha1\"\n    CRD_PLURAL = \"agentruntimes\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False) -> None\n    def deploy_agent_runtime(...) -> Dict[str, Any]\n    def get_agent_runtime(self, name: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]\n```\n\n### Runtime pattern (all runtimes in `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/`):\n\n**Common pattern:**\n1. `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\")` -- some have provider\n2. Compose services via instantiation (not dependency injection)\n3. Main public method orchestrates private methods\n4. Exceptions propagate to CLI `_handle_error`\n\n#### Runtime classes:\n- `PackRuntime` -- workspace packaging (pack command)\n- `BuildRuntime` -- image building (build command, uses `DockerService`)\n- `PublishRuntime` -- K8s deployment (publish command, uses `DockerService`, `AgentCubeProvider`, `KubernetesProvider`)\n- `InvokeRuntime` -- agent invocation (invoke command)\n- `StatusRuntime` -- agent status (status command)\n\n### Error handling pattern (from `main.py`):\n```python\ndef _handle_error(e: Exception, command_name: str, verbose: bool) -> None:\n    console.print(f\"[red]Error {command_name}: {e}[/red]\")\n    if verbose:\n        console.print_exception()\n    raise typer.Exit(1)\n```\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2869e45ddffeGrB26ud0Ek5cao","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775857941023,"end":1775858123165}}}}
